Cortex Terminal
Copyright 2026 Orellius Labs (Orel Ohayon)

This product includes software developed at Orellius Labs (https://orellius.ai).

Cortex Terminal is an AI-first multi-model terminal built with Tauri 2.0, Rust,
React 19, and xterm.js. It provides multi-model AI routing, MCP tool bridging,
and a native terminal experience in one interface.

Third-party components:
- Tauri (MIT/Apache 2.0) - https://tauri.app
- React (MIT) - https://react.dev
- xterm.js (MIT) - https://xtermjs.org
- KaTeX (MIT) - https://katex.org
- Lucide React (ISC) - https://lucide.dev
